msgid "Changing an unmanaged model to managed"
msgstr "Modification d'un modèle non géré en géré"

msgid ""
"If you want to change an unmanaged model (:attr:`managed=False <django.db."
"models.Options.managed>`) to managed, you must remove ``managed=False`` and "
"generate a migration before making other schema-related changes to the "
"model, since schema changes that appear in the migration that contains the "
"operation to change ``Meta.managed`` may not be applied."
msgstr ""
"Si vous souhaitez modifier un modèle non géré (:attr:`managed=False <django."
"db.models.Options.managed>`) en modèle géré, vous devez enlever "
"``managed=False`` et générer une migration avant de faire d'autres "
"modifications de schéma du modèle, car les modifications de schéma figurant "
"dans la même migration que celle contenant l'opération de modification de  "
